<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="idea-n">idea <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /aɪ'dɪə/    美 /aɪ'diːə/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>想法；主意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have / get an idea 
有/想到一个主意</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>the idea of (doing) sth</strong>
(做)某事的主意</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It's a silly idea to</strong> put off doing something until a future time.
把事往后推是个愚蠢的想法。</p><footer>2013 浙江</footer></div>

<p>注: 不说the idea to do sth，但可以说it is an / one's idea to do sth。  </p>
<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>大致的了解</strong></h4>
<p>a general understanding of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>have no idea</strong> what he's talking about.
我完全不明白他在说什么。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[常用复数] 意见；见解</strong></h4>
<p>sb's opinion or belief of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don't agree with his <strong>ideas about</strong> education.
我不同意他对教育的看法。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>目的；意图</strong></h4>
<p>the aim or purpose of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>The idea behind / of</strong> the activity is to encourage students to get to know each other. 
这次活动的目的是鼓励学生们相互了解。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He's saving money with <strong>the idea of</strong> buying an original novel.
他正在攒钱想买本原版小说。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>感受；印象：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>have an idea</strong> (<strong>that</strong>) I've seen her somewhere before.
我有印象好像在哪儿见过她。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.★ <strong>思想；观念：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Besides the words people speak, learning a foreign language includes their body language, dress, manners, ideas and so on.
学习外语除了学习外国人讲的语言，还包括身势语、穿着、礼仪和思想观念等。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— How far can you run without stopping?
— I <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (不知道). I've never tried. (idea)  （2013 山东改）  </li>
<li>— I'm tired. I'm taking next week off.
— <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (好主意), honey. You do need a break.  （2013 陕西改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. have no idea  2. Great / Good idea  </p></div>